metadata.name: King and Queen
metadata.description:
The design of the king and queen is a symbol of power and love between them. despite others trying to create divisions between them but they are always staring at each other in love, and any devil’s forces can’t influence them so Nothing can affect their power.
Technique: Mix media art
Acrylic, Watercolor, Marker , Metalic & Florocent color
Thanks for chosen by Keith Grossman & Nftliverpool
